	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Alla grande! <delay20 />Allora proviamo con
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />"<tag a="110" b="14" />Buooongiorno, compare!<endTag a="110" b="14" />".
<delay frames="40" />OK, <tag a="110" b="6" />?
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="60" />"<tag a="110" b="14" />Buooongiorno, compare!<endTag a="110" b="14" />"!
<delay20 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ma sì, direi che suona bene, no?<pageBreak />E pensa che non ha nemmeno
