	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ora tu e io abbiamo un saluto come
noi. <delay20 />Ma come, "come"? <delay8 />Speciale,
no? <anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />AHAHAH!<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="300" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />"<tag a="110" b="14" />Buooongiorno, compare!<endTag a="110" b="14" />"<tag a="110" b="0" />
<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Sai una cosa? <delay8 />Hai ragione.
<delay20 />È troppo bello, <tag a="110" b="6" />.</message>
	<message label="301" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />OK<tag a="110" b="0" /> Non sei per il cambiamento.<pageBreak />Ma neanche a me piace!<delay8 /> <anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Lasciamo
